  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK401">
<l>araṅkiṉṟi vaṭṭāṭi yaṟṟē nirampiya</l>
<l>nūliṉṟik kōṭṭi koḷal</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>To speak in an assembly (of the learned) without fullness of knowledge, is like playing at chess (on a board) without squares.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
